UNDE CHALA ANDAMGA 
GOPPAVI EPPUDU OKATEGA 
TELUSA DHILL ROOBA AAA. 
PAGALU CHIKATI PADDATHI GA 
KALISI UNTAYE VIDI VIDI GA.

BILLION DOLLAR FREEDOM 
SINGLE KE GA SONTHAM

KHULLAM KHULLA

HADDULUNE PETTI AAPODDU.
EE GAALI KOUGILLA LO VELA MOUANALANE DHATI.
PAPAM TELLA PILLA 
CHALI LO UNDIVELA 
THODU AYYI NENUDELA 
HALLUKU POTHUNTA

snippet.title: YAARIYAN (Official Video) Billa Sonipat Ala | Deepty | Latest Haryanvi Songs 2024 | Haryanvi Gaana
snippet.description:
White Hill Dhaakad presents the official video of Billa Sonipat Ala's new release "Yaariyan". Written and composed by Billa Sonipat Ala himself and music given by Deepty, this New Haryanvi Song is dedicated to the unbreakable bonds of friendship.
Produced by Gunbir Singh Sidhu and Manmord Singh Sidhu.

|| Meri maa ke sare ladle, Na kalla Sonipat ala re ||
Like, Comment and Share with all your friends...üòç


Credits :
Singer : Billa Sonipat Ala
Lyrics / Composer : Billa Sonipat Ala
Featuring: Billa Sonipat Ala, Vikram Sarkar, R Maan, Lakshay Malik
Music : Deepty
Mix & Master. : D Chandu
Directed By : Lakshay Malik
DOP : Arundeep Teji
Focus : Monu 
Ad : Seena Shekhpuria
Video : Team All Good
Project By : Ricky Rapria
Production : Rohit Mantro (Team All Good)
Light Equipment : Sengar Films 
Makeup : Neeraj Makeover
Edit / Di : Harmanvir Singh
Special Thanks : Ankit Duhan , Sunil Kandhal , Kd Petwar , Uday Khrab (Village Petwar)
Artist Coordination / Online Promotions : HOT (Hub Of Talent) https://www.instagram.com/hub_of_talent/
Produced by : Gunbir Singh Sidhu and Manmord Singh Sidhu




üóí Lyrics : 
Yaari mahri sabpe bhari
Yaari ya dhumme thari
Jigre ka rola hai bhai 
Palat denge duniya sari
Hojyave hai jade khade 
Ude matter hojya bade bade
Laage salami yaari mein
Na position koyi sarkari
Yaari mahri sabpe bhari
Yaari ya dhumme thari
Jigre ka rola hai bhai 
Palat denge duniya sari

Tu hasse te mera din ban ja
Tere russe te ghor andhera hai
Bhagwan dikhe manne tere mein
Re dil sone ka lehrya se
Tere jaisa yaar nahi
Yo yari dekh misal bani
Koye bole galt tere bare je
Main muh pe dedu gaal ghanni
Dil ke dhani manne yaar mile
Na ek bhi dil ka kala re 
Meri maa ke sare ladle
Na kalla sonipat ala re

Dharam veer ki jodi hai ya tode te na tuttegi
Jisdin chhod ke chale jahaan re dekhiyo andhi utthegi
Mere khater ram hai tu tera hanuman sa bhakat hu main
Bas marya jiu tere karke na itna jayada sakhat hu main
Ajya mat roos ke bhaje 
Duniya mein chhod dyu aaj ae
Fikka sab tere aage 
Rishta gehra gel teri
Kad ka karu maana maana
Kyate tu mare bahna
Muh band karde aake sabka
Na duniya sali degi tanna
Us chita pe teri gel jalu 
Teri maut ne gale ke la lyunga
Meri bhola baba sunya kare
Main sirpe duniya tha lyunga

snippet.title: DAGGER DUCHESS - New Tower Troop! (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Unlock for FREE from April 1st! No joke!

New Tower Troop enters the Arena! 
Dagger Duchess attacks her enemies by throwing a quick set of daggers when her charge is full.
Once her daggers run out, you might have to defend her while she sharpens her knives for another attack. 

Unlock Dagger Duchess now for Free during the April Season!
One more thing: Don't call her Princess.

See you in the Arena!

Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale #DaggerDuchess #TowerTroops

Due to the availability of fake colours in the market, committee members chose not to celebrate Holi, which has left all of the Gokuldham society's members deeply upset and depressed. How come everyone chose to play Holi all of a sudden? What's the deal? Watch this incredibly fantastic Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Holi special episode to find out.


Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 1364
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Watch all the exciting clips of Holi Special: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1esHln9KXStCbSKq6ifX0a

Khaie Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones #shinewithsparx
Get Ready to be Enthralled by 'Khaie' - Brought to You by Geo TV with the Cutting-Edge Innovation of Sparx Smartphone as the Exclusive Digital Presenting Partner. A Spectacular Journey Awaits

The story is a revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie, where the male members of an enemy's family are eliminated to stop the continuation of their lineage.  At the center of this age-old vendetta are Darwesh Khan, Duraab Khan, and his son Channar Khan, with Zamdaa, the daughter of Darwesh, bearing the heaviest consequences.  
Darwesh Khan is haunted by his father's murder at the hands of Duraab Khan. Seeking a peaceful life, Darwesh aims to broker a truce to end generational enmity. However, suspicions arise, and Duraab Khan and his son Channar Khan doubt Darwesh's intentions for peace.
Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

localized.description:

Khaie Last Episode 29 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones - Faysal Quraishi - Durefishan Saleem - 27th March 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khaie Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones #shinewithsparx
Get Ready to be Enthralled by 'Khaie' - Brought to You by Geo TV with the Cutting-Edge Innovation of Sparx Smartphone as the Exclusive Digital Presenting Partner. A Spectacular Journey Awaits

The story is a revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie, where the male members of an enemy's family are eliminated to stop the continuation of their lineage.  At the center of this age-old vendetta are Darwesh Khan, Duraab Khan, and his son Channar Khan, with Zamdaa, the daughter of Darwesh, bearing the heaviest consequences.  
Darwesh Khan is haunted by his father's murder at the hands of Duraab Khan. Seeking a peaceful life, Darwesh aims to broker a truce to end generational enmity. However, suspicions arise, and Duraab Khan and his son Channar Khan doubt Darwesh's intentions for peace.
Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

Written By: Saqlain Abbas
Directed By: Syed Wajahat Hussain
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Moment bridge collapses in Baltimore after cargo ship collision
snippet.description:
A portion of the Francis Scott Key Bridge in Baltimore has collapsed after a large boat collided with it early on Tuesday morning, sending multiple vehicles into the water. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ‚ñ∫ http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

At about 1.30am, a vessel crashed into the bridge, catching fire before sinking and causing multiple vehicles to fall into the water below, according to a video posted on X. ‚ÄúAll lanes closed both directions for incident on I-695 Key Bridge. Traffic is being detoured,‚Äù the Maryland Transportation Authority posted on X. The Baltimore mayor, Brandon M Scott, and and the county executive, Johnny Olszewski Jr, said emergency personnel were at the scene and rescue efforts were under way.

Episode 4042: Bawri Ke Parents Aa Gaye
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal requests Tapu to apologize to Champaklal for disrespecting him. Babita and Iyer misunderstand Jethalal's intentions as an insult to Babita. Popatlal encounters a disagreement with an auto driver. Later, Bagha and Bawri urge Jethalal to meet Bawri's parents.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Hall Ticket | Episode 3 - Result ka Din | Mini Series | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In this nail-biting episode of "Hall Ticket," anticipation reaches a fever pitch as Ujjwal and his friends eagerly await the moment of truth ‚Äì the unveiling of their board exam results! üìúüò¨
Join Ujjwal and his spirited crew as they navigate the final stretch of their academic journey, brimming with nerves, excitement, and a hint of trepidation. With each passing moment, the tension mounts as they count down the seconds until the fateful announcement.

Discover the world of 'Hall Ticket,' a series capturing the ups and downs while preparing for board exams. Join us as we follow students through late-night study sessions and last-minute reviews, sharing their nerves and excitement. 
____________________________________

Welcome to our bubble tent house, where living meets nature in the most extraordinary way! Join us on this immersive journey as we explore the enchanting world of bubble tent living. Nestled amidst breathtaking landscapes, our transparent bubble house offers a one-of-a-kind off-grid experience like no other.

In this video, we'll take you inside our bubble tent house and showcase its innovative design, allowing us to connect with the great outdoors while enjoying modern comforts. From stargazing under the night sky to waking up to panoramic views of nature's beauty, every moment in our bubble tent is a magical adventure.

Discover how we've customized our bubble tent living space for maximum comfort and sustainability, from cozy sleeping arrangements to eco-friendly amenities. Follow along as we share tips and tricks for thriving in this unique off-grid lifestyle, including energy-efficient solutions and eco-conscious practices.

Whether you're a nature enthusiast seeking a new way to experience the outdoors or simply curious about alternative living options, our bubble tent house offers inspiration and insight into a life lived close to nature. Subscribe to our channel for more adventures in bubble tent living and join us as we embrace the beauty of living in harmony with the environment. Don't forget to hit the like button and share your thoughts in the comments below!
